    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146940/extras/d1fa5327b4165652f33f3d8682659418.avif?t=1768611736\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>A paradise in the middle of nowhere finds itself missing its King...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stabilized by dedicated leadership, The town finds itself influenced by contentious generals, strange travelers, and deep seeded secretes, all threatening to return the town to chaos.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Pyrrhic Paradise is a Choice based 2D Action-RPG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a post apocalyptic fantasy town where you get the chance to dive deep and help solve the mystery of a missing King and broken system. Connect with various characters and discover what their true intentions are or add too the chaos and watch a paradise crumble</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146940/extras/5a87ad119c0396c0acb3b53c692be1b0.webp?t=1768611736\" width=1200 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146940/extras/ef8ca2b7f1f0fab997a7e701121decbd.avif?t=1768611736\" width=720 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat is fast and reactive.</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smooth controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skills to enhance strength or pierce armor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rewards aggression and consistent fighting </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deflect attacks for bonus damage and to avoid health damage</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bosses are quick and relentless.</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aggressive attack patterns that change depending on the situation </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special attacks to test the players reaction timing </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More aggressive and deadly if you kill town people or friends </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characters with unique attack patterns and temperaments </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146940/extras/d73b846b110e8f2071057526778ca72f.poster.avif?t=1768611736\" width=1170 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146940/extras/d73b846b110e8f2071057526778ca72f.webm?t=1768611736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146940/extras/d73b846b110e8f2071057526778ca72f.mp4?t=1768611736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146940/extras/5a87ad119c0396c0acb3b53c692be1b0.webp?t=1768611736\" width=1200 height=4 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2146940/extras/ef8ca2b7f1f0fab997a7e701121decbd.avif?t=1768611736\" width=720 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
